@{
    ViewBag.Title = "How to Use the App";
}

<div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="mb-4">Welcome, Learn How to use the App!</h1>
            <p class="lead">This page is where you can access all the tools you need to manage your finances effectively. You can create budgets, view budgets, input transactions, view transaction history, track your savings, and learn how to use the app.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="cardabout border-0 shadow">
                <img src="~/images/1.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Create Budgets/View Budgets">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    @*<h5 class="card-title mb-4">Create Budgets/View Budgets</h5>*@
                    <p class="card-text">Firstly, you need to create budgets for various categories like food, housing, and entertainment, among others. These budgets can be associated with a specific username. Additionally, you can view the existing budgets of different users.</p>
                    @*<a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Home</a>*@
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="cardabout border-0 shadow">
                <img src="~/images/2.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Add Transactions/View Transactions">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    @*<h5 class="card-title mb-4">Add Transactions/View Transactions</h5>*@
                    <p class="card-text">Secondly, you can add transactions by selecting a username and a relevant category such as food or housing. You also have the option to view the transaction history for a specific user and delete a transaction if necessary.</p>
                    @*<a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Home</a>*@
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="cardabout border-0 shadow">
                <img src="~/images/3.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Savings Tracker">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    @*<h5 class="card-title mb-4">Track Savings</h5>*@
                    <p class="card-text">Thirdly, you can monitor your savings for a particular username by keeping track of the remaining budget for each category. This feature helps you achieve your savings goals and make informed decisions about your spending.</p>
                    @*<a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Home</a>*@
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
